profile:
Sunshine Carpet & Flooring is Orillia's total floor covering store. Serving Simcoe and Muskoka regions for over 20 years, our family owned and operated business is dedicated
to providing the very best in style, quality and service.

Sunshine Carpet & Flooring has been voted "Best Floor Covering Store" 19 years in
a row and they continue to excel in expert knowledge and quality service.
